These are my personal dotfiles for quickshell/hyprland/niri and a modular Linux desktop.

Now organized for GNU Stow: Just use `stow -t ~ <package>` to symlink configs. and `stow -D -t ~ <package>` to remove them.

Main dependencies:

- quickshell
- hyprland
- fish
- swaync
- swayosd
- ghostty
- zen-browser
- gpu-screen-recorder
- pacman-contrib
- swayidle (idle management for Niri)
- swaylock-effects (lockscreen for Niri)
- hypridle (idle management for Hyprland)
- hyprlock (lockscreen for Hyprland)
- hyprshot (screenshots for Hyprland)
- satty (screenshot annotation/saving)
- waybar (backed-up, not used)
